Home > Entertainment > A$AP Rocky & Kendall Jenner Spotted At NYC Club A$AP Rocky & Kendall Jenner Spotted At NYC Club 0 0 Posted by Shaun M , Feb 13, 2017 at 06:22pm A$AP Rocky and Kendall Jenner stir up rumors again. 
Kendall Jenner was DJing at an NYC club last Friday for New York Fashion week and rumored beau A$AP Rocky was on hand to encourage her. The two have spotted across two continents but have yet to make anything official. 
According to US Weekly , the pair arrived together at 1 Oak nightclub. A source told the celebrity gossip mag that, "A$AP was at the table next to the DJ booth as Kendall spun all night. They all danced the night away and had an amazing time." 
The two were also spotted in France during Paris Haute Couture Fashion Week strolling around the flea markets there. And just a few days ago, they went on a double date with sister Kylie and her boyfriend Tyga . Stay tuned for more developments on this titillating story. < class="robots-nocontent" rel=""> Feb 13, 2017 at 06:22pm 0 Views
